Sammy Tillerman is Dicey's youngest brother. Seven-year-old Sammy is a rambunctious, stubborn, and good-natured. As the youngest, Sammy has the strongest and most emotional connection to Momma and in struggles more than the others to understand why she became ill and left them. Sammy works hard for causes in which he believes, but cannot be persuaded to do anything he does not want to do.Read anin-depth analysis of Sammy Tillerman.